title: Easedo Backup Advanced Server v8.6. MultiLang
description:
EASEUS Todo Backup is a complete and reliable backup and disaster recovery solution to backup system, data, files and folders, hard drive partition. It not only provides convenient user-interface to simplify your tasks but also enables you to backup and restore an image of your partitions or entire hard disk. EASEUS Todo Backup enables users to backup and restore data in multiple ways for their data security. EASEUS Todo Backup enables users to reproduce the saved state of the files, partitions or entire hard disk. Through the use of backup operation, users expect to retain their state of preservation of the files, whole hard disk or partition, and then through the restore operation, the saved state of the files, partitions or entire hard disk can be zoning restored to its state of preservation at the prior time



Changelog:

v8.6 (2015-08-06):

Work with EaseUS Backup Center seamlessly to improve the efficiency of enterprise users.
Improve the function of system recovery, universal restore and system clone on GPT drive.
Better support for Windows 10.


OS: XP/2003/Vista/2008/7/2012/8/10



INSTALLATION:



Unpack, install the application.

Block binTBConsoleUI.exe in your firewall
to enable offline activation and prevent your license from getting
blacklisted.
Allow exception of outgoing access to IP 127.0.0.1 otherwise the
application may not launch.

Use our Keygen to generate a license code and paste it in the
activation dialog.

Copy the machine code and paste it in our Keygen.
Paste the generated activation code back in the activation dialog
